*北城镇大石板村椒园<ref name="ynszxc3">{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=247765|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140314060128/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=247765 |archive-date=2014-03-14 |url-status=dead|title=红塔区北城街道办事处大石板村民委员会椒园|access-date=2016-07-24}}</ref> (自称：哩期泼)

